Description: Human Cell Atlas data sets can be discovered, previewed,
    and downloaded using the HCA data portal
    (https://data.humancellatlas.org/explore/projects) and cellxgene
    (https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/) web sites. The hca and
    cellxgenedp R / Bioconductor packages provide a more flexible and
    reproducible approach to using this data. In particular the
    packages allow direct integration of HCA data sets into the 'OSCA'
    (https://bioconductor.org/books/release/OSCA/) single-cell
    analysis workflows in R / Bioconductor.
